      "span_text": "Chromosomal integration of plasmid-mediated multiple drug resistance has been reported in S. dublin isolated in Germany and Britain; the integration of plasmid-mediated drug resistance genes into the S. typhimurium chromosome, as reported here, could be another example of the ability of the bacterial cell to conserve plasmid-mediated antimicrobial resistance genes in the absence of selective pressure."
